code: import axios from'axios';var baseUrl='/api/persons';var getAll=function getAll(){return axios.get(baseUrl).then(function(response){return response.data;});};var create=function create(newObject){return axios.post(baseUrl,newObject).then(function(response){return response.data;});};var remove=function remove(id){return axios.delete("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id));};var update=function update(id,newObject){return axios.put("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id),newObject).then(function(response){return response.data;});};export default{getAll:getAll,create:create,remove:remove,update:update};
